{
  "text": "This study's data were obtained from the randomized controlled trials that studied the effect of sialendoscopy on salivary gland function in patients with SS, [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] registered at the US National Institutes of Health (ClinicalTrials.gov; number: NCT02112019).",
